Package game.weapons

package game.weapons
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    Buyable
    Buyable interface that can be implemented and enforced classes to have all the method below Thus, the item can be purchased and added into player's inventory
    Returnable
    Returnable interface that can be implemented and enforced classes to have all the method below Thus, the item can be return and added to player's inventory
    Sellable
    Sellable interface that can be implemented and enforced classes to have all the method below Thus, the item can be sold and removed from player's inventory
